challengeName: Brivo Labs SAM API - Account Device Site Methods Doc Update
detailedRequirements:
Task Overview

The goal of this challenge is to update the input params documentation in Account, Device, and Site controllers.

Task Requirement

Document the input parameters for each method in Account, Device, and Site controller :

  • Sample from Key controller :  
  • we have 4 different type of input params :
    • path params : list the parameters set in the URL path
    • querystring params : list any querystring parameter
    • body params : list the body of the request in details
    • custom headers : should list any custom header read by the method

API Code

Provided in challenge forums.

Deliverables

Patch file of the changes. with text file including any notes to the reviewer.
